20
00:01:59,000 --> 00:01:59,879
Yifan!

21
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,719
It's been so many years.

22
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,589
I'll help you get the key.

23
00:02:03,590 --> 00:02:04,160
Let's go.

24
00:02:04,180 --> 00:02:04,790
Okay.

25
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:05,599
Huan'er.

26
00:02:05,620 --> 00:02:06,870
Do you remember Aunt Lin Yifan?

27
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,759
She used to carry you
when you were little.

28
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,599
Say hello.

29
00:02:10,599 --> 00:02:11,520
Hello, Aunt Yifan.

30
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,360
She doesn't remember.

31
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,420
She was so little back then.
How could she remember?

32
00:02:14,460 --> 00:02:15,040
This way.

33
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:18,780
No problem.

34
00:02:18,780 --> 00:02:20,700
I'll finish the paperwork
before I get off work.

35
00:02:20,700 --> 00:02:21,150
Thank you.

36
00:02:21,159 --> 00:02:21,960
See you later.

37
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:22,400
Okay.

38
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,240
Huan'er.

39
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,310
I'm going to the hospital.

40
00:02:24,310 --> 00:02:25,300
Watch over things for me.

41
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:26,280
Lina, I'll go with you.

42
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:26,940
Okay, Yifan.

43
00:02:53,879 --> 00:02:54,960
Watch my stuff for me.

44
00:03:34,039 --> 00:03:34,719
Hey...

45
