46
00:03:50,039 --> 00:03:50,319
Here.

47
00:03:50,319 --> 00:03:51,360
Use this to wipe it off.

48
00:03:53,719 --> 00:03:54,479
Thanks.

49
00:03:58,640 --> 00:03:59,630
Did you just move in?

50
00:03:59,660 --> 00:04:00,960
I haven't seen you before.

51
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:03,540
My home is right here.

52
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,919
I guess we're neighbors now.

53
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:06,919
Thanks.

54
00:04:07,140 --> 00:04:07,960
Nice to meet you.

55
00:04:07,980 --> 00:04:08,490
My name is...

56
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,120
Bye-bye.

57
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:15,759
(This guy...)

58
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,480
(Why is he so weird?)

59
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:26,360
