73
00:04:54,399 --> 00:04:55,120
Chen Huan'er,

74
00:04:55,439 --> 00:04:56,519
tell us how you feel.

75
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:58,600
I...

76
00:04:59,439 --> 00:05:00,279
I'm so excited.

77
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:01,759
Louder.

78
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,120
I...

79
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:05,120
I'm so excited.

80
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,620
